The author of [Spike Japan](http://spikejapan.wordpress.com/) decided to spend
last week's national holidays in the Fukushima prefecture. In his latest post
he [chronicles his journey
](http://spikejapan.wordpress.com/2011/05/08/holiday-in-fukushima-to-the-zone-
of-exclusion/) [en] to the tsunami hit area and its surroundings.

